A followup review. I suspect that this file contains a virus. Now, I know the keygen shows up as a virus, but I found a MBR virus called rikvm on my computer after installing. Now, I can't be 100% sure it was from this file, but my computer started running very slowly after installing. I was able to clean it with Norton Power Eraser- Norton Security Suite did not pick it up.

Virus Total Report:

https://www.virustotal.com/file/9d61673202c08f2105077bcb740cf3420e412ab8b02ada79e3c4f66bc17f1b48/analysis/1329641787/

File is safe.....
